title: Smart Succulent Pork Tenderloin  with Fresh Cucumber and Tomato Relish
description: There's so much to love about this seared pork on a fluffy bed of couscous, topped with fresh cucumber and tomato relish. The generous sprinkling of crumbled feta cheese over top adds to the flavour explosion.

